::Hot Rod::

He looked at Eclipse.
"Optimus Prime evil?! Who? How? You mean Primal Prime? Hot Rod hadnt
believed that Primal was Optimus. But this was still disturbing.
"Tell me everything. If that was really Optimus, then I'm the best bot
to deal with it."
